jsten/top-100-jaaroverzichten/1986 |title=Top 100-Jaaroverzicht van 1986 |language=Dutch |publisher=Dutch Top 40 |accessdate=21 August 2019}}</ref>\n| 64\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Netherlands (Single Top 100)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://dutchcharts.nl/jaaroverzichten.asp?year=1986&cat=s |title=Jaaroverzichten \u2013 Single 1986 |website=dutchcharts.nl |language=Dutch |accessdate=21 August 2019}}</ref>\n| 63\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand (Recorded Music NZ)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=3875 |title=Top Selling Singles of 1986 |publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]] |accessdate=21 August 2019}}</ref>\n| 6\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| South Africa (Springbok Radio)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rock.co.za/files/sahits_1986.html |title=Top 20 Hit Singles of 1986 |website=The South African Rock Encyclopedia |accessdate=2 September 2018}}</ref>\n| 20\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Switzerland (Schweizer Hitparade)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://hitparade.ch/charts/jahreshitparade/1986 |title=Schweizer Jahreshitparade 1986 |website=hitparade.ch |language=German |accessdate=21 August 2019}}</ref>\n| 5\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US ''Billboard'' Hot 100<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/1986/hot-100-songs |title=Hot 100 Songs \u2013 Year-End 1986 |work=Billboard |accessdate=21 August 2019}}</ref>\n| 38\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US Dance Club Songs (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/1986/dance-club-songs |title=Dance Club Songs \u2013 Year-End 1986 |work=Billboard |accessdate=21 August 2019}}</ref>\n| 21\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US ''Cash Box'' Top 100<ref>{{cite web |url=https://cashboxmagazine.com/archives/80s_files/1986YESP.html |title=The Cash Box Year-End Charts: 1986 \u2013 Top 100 Pop Singles |work=Cash Box |date=27 December 1986 |accessdate=21 August 2019}}</ref>\n| 43\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| West Germany (Official German Charts)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/single-jahr/for-d